Package com.ajah.user.account

Accounts are billing/management entities.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Account An Account corresponds to a billing or non-person entity.
AccountStatus All accounts must be in some state, which determines the permitted operations.
AccountType All accounts must be of some type, which determines the permitted operations.
 

Class Summary
AccountId A wrapper around a String for typesafe account IDs.
 

Package com.ajah.user.account Description

Accounts are billing/management entities. A User has access to Accounts. A user may belong to zero or more accounts, and an account may have one or more users.
